hopobject.body: A few months indemand.medicines.org.uk “The president is going to explore whether the Russian option is real. If it is, that would be good,” said Sen. Lamar Alexander, R-Tenn., who had intended to oppose the Syria strike. “If there is a diplomatic solution that would remove chemical weapons from Syria that we could enforce that would be good for our country and it would be good for the world … we should know that in a week or two.”
